            text: "While valuing family over money is a good ethical baseline, it is not the highest spiritual truth. The highest truth is valuing Dharma (Universal Order) over both family and money. Arjuna's reasoning, while sweet to the human ear, is spiritually short-sighted because it ignores justice.",
