          title: "Inner Conflicts",
          text: "Stop arguing with yourself. Stop debating whether you made the right choice five years ago. Let the mind drop all the conflicting voices (śruti-vipratipannā). Take a breath, anchor yourself in the present moment (Samadhi), and step into the power of a quiet mind.",
