            text: "An immovable intellect does not mean a paralyzed body. Remember, Krishna is teaching this so Arjuna can fight a world war! A person in Samadhi is the most effective person in the room. Because their mind is completely still, they see reality exactly as it is, allowing them to make flawless, lightning-fast decisions without the drag of anxiety or ego.",
