            title: "Strategic Retraction",
            text: "If a tortoise stays in its shell forever, it starves. The goal is not isolation; the goal is autonomy. You use your senses to do your duty in the world, but you retain the sovereign ability to retract them the second the world threatens your spiritual alignment.",
