            title: "Prefrontal Override",
            text: "Rationally, the brain is processing sensory input (visual, auditory) without activating the mesolimbic dopamine pathway (craving) or the amygdala (aversion). The prefrontal cortex (Vidheyātmā) maintains top-down control. The organism processes the data of the world strictly for utility and objective appreciation, eliminating the energetic tax of compulsive reactions.",
