          text: "We are obsessed with 'leaving a legacy' and making sure everyone remembers our name forever. The Gita flips this. The highest spiritual master desires to leave absolutely no karmic footprint. They do massive, beautiful work for the world, but they want their egoic signature to dissolve completely. True greatness is anonymous in spirit.",
