            title: "Activation Energy",
            text: "In chemistry, a reaction requires 'Activation Energy' to break existing bonds and form new, stable ones. Rationally, 'Karma-jān' represents this activation energy. You cannot transform the heavy, toxic bonds of the ego into the liberated state of the Yogi without injecting massive amounts of deliberate kinetic energy (Karma) into the system. Inaction yields no transformation.",
