            text: "You do not see all beings inside your *Ego* (Ahamkara). You see all beings inside the *Atman* (the formless, silent Soul). To achieve this vision, the ego must be completely destroyed. Megalomania is the inflation of the ego; this vision is the total annihilation of it.",
