            text: "The goal of the Gita is not to get superpowers, levitate, or see visions. The ultimate, highest prize in the spiritual universe is 'Parāṃ Śāntim'—an unshakable, adamantine, crystalline Peace. A peace that cannot be disturbed by cancer, bankruptcy, or death. That is the true gold.",
