            text: "The word 'Vaśam' implies control and domestication, not murder. If you use violent frustration to stop a thought, you are just replacing a distracting thought with an angry thought. The retrieval must be firm, objective, and entirely devoid of emotional frustration. It is a clean, mechanical reset.",
