            title: "The Sacred Complaint",
            text: "In many dogmatic traditions, arguing with God is a sin. In the Gita, arguing with God is the mechanism of revelation. Arjuna's complaint is not a sin; it is a sacred inquiry that forces the philosophy out of the clouds and down into the mud of human application.",
