            text: "Brahma is immensely powerful and highly revered as the first created being and the head of spiritual lineages. Arjuna is using Brahma as the ultimate benchmark. He is saying, 'Brahma is the greatest being we know of, and You are even greater than him!' It establishes a hierarchy of profound respect, culminating in the Absolute.",
